<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Navbar Styles */
    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(20, 20, 50, 0.9);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 5%;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .navbar a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background: #00adb5;
      color: #fff;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Container Styles */
    .container {
      background: rgba(40, 40, 70, 0.95);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      text-align: center;
      animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: #f7f7f7;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #f7f7f7;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      100% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(-100px);
        opacity: 0;
      }

      100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="./">Home</a>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Bankist App</h2>
    <p>A modern banking application built using JavaScript, EJS (Embedded JavaScript Templates), and SQLite. This project demonstrates a fully functional banking application, showcasing key features such as money transfers and transaction history.</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
